Package xbot.common.properties

Class PreferenceStorage

java.lang.Object
xbot.common.properties.PreferenceStorage
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITableProxy, PermanentStorage
@Singleton public class PreferenceStorage extends Object implements PermanentStorage
This saves properties to the robot using WPI's built-in Preferences library. This stores them in a simple key-value pair on the robot, in a file called /home/lvuser/networktables.ini.
